<div class="section">
    <h2>Our Facilities</h2>

    <h3>Space for Development</h3>
    <p>
        The Centre offers an ideal environment and resources for teaching, training, or organizational planning.
    </p>

    <h3>Conferences and Seminars</h3>
    <p>
        We offer 5 fully carpeted, air-conditioned conference rooms with capacities ranging from 25 to 200 people.
    </p>

    <h3>Accommodations</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>34 bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms and air-conditioning.</li>
        <li>26 bedrooms with two-piece bathrooms and shared shower rooms at the end of the hallways.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Food and Hospitality</h3>
    <p>
        Our in-house chef and kitchen staff prepare all meals. We offer:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Three full-course meals daily.</li>
        <li>Three coffee breaks.</li>
        <li>Platters of food served directly to each table.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Resources and Recreation</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Flip charts, audio-visual equipment, and a photocopier.</li>
        <li>A covered swimming pool available in the summer.</li>
        <li>Acres of lawn for outdoor activities and relaxation.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Meetings and Conventions</h3>
    <p>
        We welcome groups and organizations to rent our facilities for meetings, conferences, or retreats. We can accommodate:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Single-day events.</li>
        <li>Overnight accommodations for extended events.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        For inquiries about hosting your group or convention, please contact: 
        <a href="mailto:office@qoa.ca">office@qoa.ca</a>
    </p>
</div>
